com.nokia.maps.sharing

Class SharingManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.nokia.maps.sharing.SharingManager

  • public abstract class SharingManager
extends java.lang.Object
    This class used to create URLs that can be shared with other users. The MapCanvas, Locations and Places can be converted into a URL that can be shared off the device. All the methods in this class are synchronous. All methods return a URL as a String on success, null otherwise.
